    <body>
         <section id="release-1.3.0" name="Release 1.3.0">
            <p>Features:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    Added
                    <a href="apidocs/index.html?biz/gabrys/maven/plugin/util/parameter/ParametersLogBuilder.html">
                        ParametersLogBuilder
                    </a>
                    which allows to log Mojos parameters values
                </li>
                <li>
                    Added protected method
                    <a href="apidocs/index.html?biz/gabrys/maven/plugin/util/io/AntFileScanner.html">
                        AntFileScanner#createDirectoryScanner()
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    Added protected method
                    <a href="apidocs/index.html?biz/gabrys/maven/plugin/util/io/RegexFileScanner.html">
                        RegexFileScanner#createFileFilter(File, String[], String[])
                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <p>Bugs:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    Fixed incorrect implementation of method
                    <a href="apidocs/index.html?biz/gabrys/maven/plugin/util/timer/Time.html">
                        Time#toString()
                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>
         <section id="release-1.2" name="Release 1.2">
            <p>Features:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    Allow access to all classes from
                    <a href="http://maven-plugin-utils.projects.gabrys.biz/1.2/apidocs/index.html?biz/gabrys/maven/plugin/util/io/package-summary.html">biz.gabrys.maven.plugin.util.io</a>
                    package
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section id="release-1.1" name="Release 1.1">
            <p>Bugs:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    Corrected
                    <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Double-checked_locking">
                        double-checked locking
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>Optimization of call logger instructions</li>
                <li>Added missing <a href="http://maven-plugin-utils.projects.gabrys.biz/1.1/apidocs/">JavaDocs</a></li>
            </ul>
            <p><a href="http://maven-plugin-utils.projects.gabrys.biz/1.1/">See documentation</a></p>
        </section>
        <section id="release-1.0" name="Release 1.0">
            <p>Initial release.</p>
            <p><a href="http://maven-plugin-utils.projects.gabrys.biz/1.0/">See documentation</a></p>
        </section>
    </body>
